         <abstract id="aspace_beb72b0d7ddc6a459c90b5eb5ec043bf">Correspondence, memoranda, reports, minutes, and other papers relating to the Connecticut Pesticide Investigating Committee. This committee was chaired by Anthony E. Wallace and one its members was David Martyn Smith.</abstract>
